re permissive 6 seconds. This change allows for a slower crossing without generating alarms. The test è immediate: I ask the same user to try again, and the transit occurs without any problems. I explain the change to the customer, who appreciates the personalized solution. The intervention is completed without touching a single physical component." } }" },
